===Noun===
'''apple''' (''plural:'' '''apples''')

# A [[tree]] of the [[genus]] ''[[Malus]]''; the apple tree. [[Category: Trees]]
# A [[fruit]] produced by an apple tree.[[Category:Fruits]]
# The [[wood]] of the apple tree.
#(''in plural; Cockney rhyming slang'') Short for '''[[apples and pears]]''' (which see).
# {{baseball}} {{slang}} an 1800s baseball term meaning the [[ball]]

